Questions:
Which of the following procedures is considered experimental in the treatment of advanced gastric cancer patients with D2 surgery in this study?
A) Standard D2 surgical resection of gastric cancer;
B) Postoperative systemic adjuvant chemotherapy with SOX/XELOX regimen;
C) Hyperthermic intraperitoneal chemotherapy (HIPEC) using either paclitaxel or lobaplatin;
D) Routine blood tests and biochemical checks before and after chemotherapy.

Correct answer: C
